<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>With ZF-1936 (<a href="http://framework.zend.com/issues/browse/ZF-1936">http://framework.zend.com/issues/browse/ZF-1936</a>) is impossible to retrieve the complete Zend_Translate_Adapter::$_translate protected property without a foreach cycle over Zend_Translate_Adapter::getList() and the usage of Zend_Translate_Adapter::getMessage() method.
It's required a method to retrieve the entire dictionary.
I propose Zend_Translate_Adapter::getDictionary().</p>

